The experimental impulse-rapier backend links a first-party native shim against Rust crates.

Direct Rust dependencies:

- rapier3d: Apache-2.0
  Repository: https://github.com/dimforge/rapier
  License: https://github.com/dimforge/rapier/blob/master/LICENSE

- jni: MIT OR Apache-2.0
  Repository: https://github.com/jni-rs/jni-rs
  License files: https://github.com/jni-rs/jni-rs/tree/master/licenses

Run `cargo metadata` in `impulse-rapier/src/main/rust` when producing a release artifact to audit transitive crate licenses.
